title: Violence Agency Act 2023 (No. 31 of 2023), hereby order as follows:
heading: 2. The 1st day of January 2024 is appointed to be the establishment day
text_raw:
2. The 1st day of January 2024 is appointed to be the establishment day 
for the purposes of the Domestic, Sexual and Gender-Based Violence Agency 
Act 2023 (No. 31 of 2023). 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

20 December, 2023. 

HELEN MCENTEE, 
Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
"Iris Oifigiúil" of 22nd December, 2023.
